HEIGHT="83" border="0" alt="the code"></A>
</p>

<p>
<font size="-1">
*from Trinh T. Minh-Ha <EM>When the Moon Waxes Red: Representation,
Gender and Cultural Politics</EM>.  New York: Routledge, 1991.
<BR>
Ebsdorf World Map, 13th century,  from <EM>Geographie Du Monde Au
Moyen Age et a la Renaissance</EM>, edited by Monique Pelletier.
Paris: C.T.H.S. 1989.
<BR>
All permissions have been requested.
</font>
